I"<p>Following up on our last talk on Time Series, we decided to implement machine learning techniques to forecast the IBM stock price.</p>

<p>The first step was to get the historical data (for the last 5 years). We obtained this via the Yahoo Finances webpage. We then prepared the data to be fed into an LSTM neural network. We implemented the LSTM network using the Keras library.</p>

